<!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_registers#Mask_.28.242001.29_.3E_write">http://wiki.nesdev.com/w/index.php/PPU_ ... _.3E_write</a><!-- m --><br /><br />The line states that writing #$30 to $2001 will produce a monochrome display. It seems that is incorrect. Writing #$1F will produce the monochrome display. Writing #$30 will only remove the background rendering and intensify red.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4326">67726e</a> — Tue Dec 14, 2010 5:12 pm</p><hr />
